{"content": "I need to multiply 648\u2089 \u00d7 636\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n648\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 486 + 36 + 8 = 530\u2081\u2080\n\n636\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 486 + 27 + 6 = 519\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n530 \u00d7 519 = 275,070\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n275070 \u00f7 9 = 30563 r 3\n30563 \u00f7 9 = 3395 r 8\n3395 \u00f7 9 = 377 r 2\n377 \u00f7 9 = 41 r 8\n41 \u00f7 9 = 4 r 5\n4 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 4\n\nReading from bottom to top: 458283\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n458283\u2089 = 4\u00d759049 + 5\u00d76561 + 8\u00d7729 + 2\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 3\u00d71\n= 236196 + 32805 + 5832 + 162 + 72 + 3\n= 275070\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n458283", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 416}